`4++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++``
`8Keywords``   : Buy
`8Categories`` : 
`4++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++``

`8Syntax:`` 

 * buy <item>
 * buy <number>*<item>

 This is the command you use in a shop to purchase items.  You can buy a single
item with the first syntax example.  To purchase multiples of the same item,
such as 10 recall scrolls, you would type "buy 10*recall". 

 See also List, Sell, and Value.

`4++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++``
